race.comment: WHOPPI DEVERE (1) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (25.70) at Shepparton in a Maiden over 450m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can go on with it. PHOTOGENIC (2) is a Gavin Clifton-trained newcomer by Photo Man out of Golden Skyrocket. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Betting to provide the best guide to his chances. REALITY UTE (3) makes his debut without a trial but profiles well for first outing. Can measure up. LIDDELL (7) is by Whiskey Riot out of Sekola making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles well so pay to keep very safe.
